[
    {
        "content": "<p>I want to recompile 6.8 kernel on my Ubuntu server with maximum Rust support.</p>\n<p>cp &lt;/boot/.curently_running_config&gt; .config</p>\n<p>check:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">ubuntu2404arm</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">headers</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">40</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">generic</span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rustavailable</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">available</span><span class=\"o\">!</span>\n<span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">ubuntu2404arm</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">headers</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">40</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">generic</span><span class=\"p\">#</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code>make menuconfig</code></p>\n<p>Rust options are not visible (it is visible if I build the config with <code>make defconfig</code>)</p>\n<p>How to fix that?</p>",
        "id": 462747896,
        "sender_full_name": "Nikolai Shv",
        "timestamp": 1723799911
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Have you tried</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">menuconfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>?</p>",
        "id": 462749063,
        "sender_full_name": "Dirk Behme",
        "timestamp": 1723800227
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"669329\">Dirk Behme</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/Rust.20options.20are.20not.20visible.20in.20.60menuconfig.60/near/462749063\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Have you tried</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">menuconfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Same - no rust options in menu:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">ubuntu2404arm</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">clean</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;&amp;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mrproper</span>\n<span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">ubuntu2404arm</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">olddefconfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ARCH</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">arm64</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">basic</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">fixdep</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">conf</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">confdata</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">expr</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">LEX</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">lexer</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">lex</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">YACC</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">parser</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tab</span><span class=\"p\">.[</span><span class=\"n\">ch</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">lexer</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">lex</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">menu</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">parser</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tab</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">preprocess</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">symbol</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTCC</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">util</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HOSTLD</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kconfig</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">conf</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">using</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">defaults</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">found</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">boot</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">40</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">generic</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">configuration</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">written</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">config</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span>\n<span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">ubuntu2404arm</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rustavailable</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">available</span><span class=\"o\">!</span>\n<span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">ubuntu2404arm</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">6.8.0</span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">menuconfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ARCH</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">arm64</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/qFSNyolDkWIhcddw8bcjG51i/Screenshot-2024-08-16-at-5.48.46PM.png\">Screenshot-2024-08-16-at-5.48.46PM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/qFSNyolDkWIhcddw8bcjG51i/Screenshot-2024-08-16-at-5.48.46PM.png\" title=\"Screenshot-2024-08-16-at-5.48.46PM.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1426x1852\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/35136/qFSNyolDkWIhcddw8bcjG51i/Screenshot-2024-08-16-at-5.48.46PM.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
